Sentencas: A glass based on Y2O3-BaO-SiO2-B2O3-Al2O3 (named YBA) has been investigated as sealant for planar solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs).
Titulo: Y2O3-BaO-SiO2-B2O3-Al2O3 glass sealant for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The YBA glass has been systematically characterized by differential thermal analysis.
Titulo: Y2O3-BaO-SiO2-B2O3-Al2O3 glass sealant for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: dilatometer, scanning electron microscopy, impedance analysis, and open circuit voltage to examine their suitability as sealant.
Titulo: Y2O3-BaO-SiO2-B2O3-Al2O3 glass sealant for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The coefficient of thermal expansion of YBA is 11.64 x 10(-6) K-1 between 323 and 873 K.
Titulo: Y2O3-BaO-SiO2-B2O3-Al2O3 glass sealant for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The resistivity is 9.1 x 10(4) Omega cm at 800 degrees C.
Titulo: Y2O3-BaO-SiO2-B2O3-Al2O3 glass sealant for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The glass sealant is found to be well adhered with other cell components, such as electrolytes and stainless steels, at an optimum sealing temperature of 800 C. All measured results showed that the YBA glass appears to be a promising sealant for SOFCs.
Titulo: Y2O3-BaO-SiO2-B2O3-Al2O3 glass sealant for solid oxide fuel cells
